import { library} from '@fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core';
import {
  faSortDown,
  faPlus,
  faMinus,
  faPlay,
  faChevronDown,
  faChevronRight,
  faChevronLeft,
  faPlayCircle,
  faPlusCircle,
  faInfoCircle,
  faSearch,
} from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons';
import {
  faFacebook,
  faGoogle,
} from '@fortawesome/free-brands-svg-icons';

library.add(
  faFacebook,
  faGoogle,
  faSortDown,
  faPlus,
  faMinus,
  faPlay,
  faChevronDown,
  faChevronRight,
  faChevronLeft,
  faPlayCircle,
  faPlusCircle,
  faInfoCircle,
  faSearch,
);
